    <title>Group_radius Module</title>

    <section id="group_radius.overview">
	<title>Overview</title>
	<para>
	    This module export functions necessary for group membership
	    checking over radius. There is a database table that contains list
	    of users and groups they belong to. The table is used by functions
	    of this module.
	</para>
    </section>

